.slick-widget-testimonials.wow.fadeIn
	.slick-slider.carousel-child#child-carousel(
	data-for='.carousel-parent',
	data-arrows='true',
	data-loop='true',
	data-dots='false',
	data-swipe='true',
	data-items='1',
	data-sm-items='3',
	data-md-items='5',
	data-lg-items='5',
	data-xl-items='5',
	data-center-mode='true',
	data-slide-to-scroll='1' )
		.item.wow-outer: +img( 'testimonials-person-1-96x96' ).wow.slideInLeft
		.item.wow-outer: +img( 'testimonials-person-2-96x96' ).wow.slideInLeft
		.item.wow-outer: +img( 'testimonials-person-3-96x96' ).wow.slideInLeft
		.item.wow-outer: +img( 'testimonials-person-4-96x96' ).wow.slideInLeft
		.item.wow-outer: +img( 'testimonials-person-5-96x96' ).wow.slideInLeft
		.item.wow-outer: +img( 'testimonials-person-6-96x96' ).wow.slideInLeft


	// Slick Carousel
	.slick-slider.carousel-parent(
	data-arrows='false',
	data-loop='true',
	data-dots='false',
	data-swipe='false',
	data-items='1',
	data-fade='true',
	data-child='#child-carousel',
	data-for='#child-carousel' )
		.item
			// Quote Light 1
			blockquote.quote-light
				cite.quote-light-cite Kelly McMillan
				p.quote-light-caption Regular client
				+quote-mark.quote-light-mark
				.quote-light-text: p I could not be more impressed with your services. Your professional engravers made my daughter’s trophy look evem more impressive than it was. Thank you for a great job you delivered!

		.item
			// Quote Light 2
			blockquote.quote-light
				cite.quote-light-cite Harold Barnett
				p.quote-light-caption Regular client
				+quote-mark.quote-light-mark
				.quote-light-text: p I have been looking for a good engraving studio for a long time as I often need dog tags of high quality. You carefully listened to all my requests and completed the task quickly and efficiently. Thank you!

		.item
			// Quote Light 3
			blockquote.quote-light
				cite.quote-light-cite Albert Webb
				p.quote-light-caption Regular client
				+quote-mark.quote-light-mark
				.quote-light-text: p My daughter liked her new engraved present very much! Your experts did a w0nderful job on engraving her portrait on cherry wood. Their creativity and unique approach are absolutely unmatched!

		.item
			// Quote Light 4 
			blockquote.quote-light
				cite.quote-light-cite Samantha Lee
				p.quote-light-caption Regular client
				+quote-mark.quote-light-mark
				.quote-light-text: p I have worked with dozens of engravers before but none of them are as experienced as Graver’s team. Their work on trophies for the local championship was quick yet unbelievably professional.

		.item
			// Quote Light 5
			blockquote.quote-light
				cite.quote-light-cite Bill Warner
				p.quote-light-caption Regular client
				+quote-mark.quote-light-mark
				.quote-light-text: p We have quite an intricate logo but your team did a great job on engraving it for our new office. Thank you! I hope to work with you more in the future and will definitely recommend you to my colleagues.

		.item
